title: The Big Suey: Toenly Fans
description:
Mike Ryan's nails are still black from his themed birthday party as he breaks down UM's loss to the North Carolina Tar Heels. Greg Cote is considering selling his toe nail as a NFT. Plus, Justin Tucker's excellence, Stugotz wants a "gut guy" on analytics staffs, a SWAC off, and more.
